name: One year subscription
description:
Six cards delivered to your door, every three months, for one year (24 cards all together, four deliveries.)

Each delivery will be a selection of seasonal designs hand picked appropriately for any upcoming holidays.  Please specify if you would like any particular designs, as well as when you would like your subscription to start.

Free shipping!

name: Half year subscription
description:
Six cards delivered to your door, every three months, for half a year.  (Twelve cards in total, two deliveries.)

The deliveries will be a selection of seasonal designs appropriate for any upcoming holidays.  Please specify if you would like any particular designs, and when you would like your first delivery to start. 

Free shipping!

name: Just one delivery, please
description: Six cards delivered to your door, next week.  Will be a selection of seasonal designs appropriate for any upcoming holidays.  Please specify if you would like any particular designs.
